The paper discusses the flow of knowledge from a national research system, which suggests it may fall under the Digital Libraries (cs.DL) sub-category. Additionally, the methodology used to examine knowledge flows across fields and countries may involve techniques from Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Social Networks (cs.SI). The paper also mentions measuring field comparative advantage, which could relate to topics in Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and System and Data Analysis (cs.SD).
